==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: editorialize
<hw>ed`i*to"ri*al*ize</hw> <pos>v. i.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>to write an
opinion in an editorial in a publication.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>to insert personal opinions into an article or
statement that is supposed to be an objective statement of
facts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Editorially</ent>⟦br⟧
